      • add

        private void add​(int x,
                 int y,
                 float alphaFade,
                 @NotNull
                 Note note)
        Paint a note to the specified position. If there is already a note, the colors will be added. But only the last added note will be associated. The invoking method should ensure the following (x < 0) || (x ≥ this.getWidth()) || (y < 0) || (y ≥ this.getHeight()) as this method does not check this!
        Parameters:
        x -
        y -
        alphaFade - a value in [0, 1] that is multiplied with the default alpha value; with this, the fading of the note throughout its duration is realized
        note -
